{"tid":2402614,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國放水第三集","createTime":"2021-02-10T13:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T13:57:31.000Z","uid":391458,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"719232350b40dd075be3423f2729fb44247b409e","tid":2402614,"uid":391458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"美國史無前例咁樣放第二輪水，自己估吓Bitcoin, Ethereum，黃金同埋白銀 會升到上去乜嘢位？用膝頭哥都諗到啦！<br />\n<br />\n覺得一年內美國可以收水咩？ 乜嘢都係睇水流。到佢話唔再放水或者收水嗰陣時，Bitcoin, Ethereum仲喺度狂升，啲人喺度又話乜嘢大時代又話經濟完全回復，嗰陣時先係最伏，先係最後瘋狂。<br />\n😎😎😎😎🚀🚀🚀🚀🚀💎💎💎💎💎🙌🙌🙌🙌<br />\nQE alone, and QE plus fiscal spending, are two very different things when it comes to affecting broad money supply.<br />\n<br />\nLyn Alden 2/6/21<br />\n<br />\nBroad money is now going vertical...<br />\n<br />\nBase money = 以前嗰啲 QE, 啲錢大多數留喺銀行體系，唔會出街<br />\nBroad money supply = 出咗街啲錢，今次係洪水泛濫🤣🤣🤣🤣🤣😰😰😰😰😰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-fed-mester-idUSKBN2A823E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-fed-mester-idUSKBN2A823E&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=0409427f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-fed-mester-idUSKBN2A823E&h=37cb50a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-fed-mester-idUSKBN2A823E</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgzMzUE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgzMzUE.png&h=3bd0f7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有排玩😅😅😅"},{"pid":"5cbbf7653ff29440e5a0565b96b9258be2d37ffb","tid":2402614,"uid":391458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:57:31.000Z","msg":"Real Yields 正正加速向負數進行。個後果係點盲嘅都知道。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARqv1Aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARqv1Aa.jpg&h=1b3f2b29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDXY 美匯指數之前只不過係小陽春，嚟緊先仲大鑊....<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pbr3